{{#arraymap:{{#show:Category:{{{1|}}}|?Show backlinks for|link=none|sep=,}}|,|@@prop@@|{{Category/backlink-row | prop=@@prop@@ | label={{#show:@@prop@@|?Inverse property label|default={{PAGENAME:@@prop@@}}}} }}|\n}}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Renders backlink rows for properties linking to the current page,
discovered dynamically from the category's `Show backlinks for`
annotation.

Composes Category/backlink-row, one per discovered property. Wraps in
an aggregate count check so the "Backlinks" header only appears when
at least one property has results.

This is the dynamic-discovery path. Auto-generated dispatcher
templates bypass it: the generator pre-builds the entire backlinks
block (header + rows) and passes it as `backlink_section=` to
Category/sidebox or Category/table, which emits it directly. That
avoids the runtime `#show:Category:X|?Show backlinks for` and the
per-property `#show:@@prop@@|?Inverse property label` lookups.

Use this template directly only in hand-written custom display
wikitext when you want runtime discovery.

Parameter 1: category name (without namespace prefix).
</noinclude>
